        },
        {
          "alias": "title",
          "culture": "en-US",
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Security Policy"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "contentTypeKey": "7933a097-e795-4929-9746-d802b4ed8595",
      "key": "b99234ce-48c7-4011-8346-2115db874635",
      "values": [
        {
          "alias": "title",
          "culture": "en-US",
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Built-in Security Features"
        },
        {
          "alias": "content",
          "culture": "en-US",
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": {
            "contentData": [
              {
                "contentTypeKey": "be80a795-b398-4baa-860a-ee68b7124f11",
                "key": "dd05202b-0d06-465d-a5e2-d7549f319a6c",
                "values": [
                  {
                    "alias": "richtext",
                    "culture": "en-US",
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": {
                      "blocks": {
                        "contentData": [],
                        "settingsData": [],
                        "expose": [],
                        "layout": {}
                      },
                      "markup": "\u003Cp\u003EuTPro includes the following security hardening out of the box:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EHTTP Security Headers\u003C/strong\u003E: X-Content-Type-Options, X-Frame-Options, Referrer-Policy, Permissions-Policy\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EHSTS\u003C/strong\u003E: Strict-Transport-Security in production (1 year, includeSubDomains)\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESecure Sessions\u003C/strong\u003E: HttpOnly, Secure, SameSite=Strict cookies\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ERequest Limits\u003C/strong\u003E: 128MB max upload, protection against oversized payloads\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EDomain Policy\u003C/strong\u003E: Configurable domain allowlist with wildcard matching\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EData Protection\u003C/strong\u003E: Encryption keys with 90-day automatic rotation\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EXSS Prevention\u003C/strong\u003E: HTML-encoded meta tag values in SEO output\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EError Pages\u003C/strong\u003E: noindex/nofollow to prevent search engine indexing of error pages\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003C/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E"
                    }
                  }
                ]
              }
            ],
            "settingsData": [],
            "expose": [
              {
                "contentKey": "dd05202b-0d06-465d-a5e2-d7549f319a6c",
                "culture": "en-US",
                "segment": null
              }
            ],
            "layout": {
              "Umbraco.BlockList": [
                {
                  "contentKey": "dd05202b-0d06-465d-a5e2-d7549f319a6c",
                  "contentUdi": null,
                  "settingsKey": null,
                  "settingsUdi": null
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "contentTypeKey": "7933a097-e795-4929-9746-d802b4ed8595",
      "key": "0c126f80-121b-4f41-b97a-f2d67bc8859b",
      "values": [
        {
          "alias": "content",
          "culture": "en-US",
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": {
            "contentData": [
              {
                "contentTypeKey": "be80a795-b398-4baa-860a-ee68b7124f11",
                "key": "b0146e85-c0a7-4be4-9b1e-f5f56dc37077",
                "values": [
                  {
                    "alias": "richtext",
                    "culture": "en-US",
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": {
                      "blocks": {
                        "contentData": [],
                        "settingsData": [],
                        "expose": [],
                        "layout": {}
                      },
                      "markup": "\u003Cp\u003EIf you discover a security vulnerability, please do not disclose it publicly; instead, report it through the following official channels:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003EEmail: \u003Ca data-router-slot=\u0022disabled\u0022 href=\u0022mailto:thientu@t4vn.com\u0022 type=\u0022external\u0022\u003E\u003Cu\u003Ethientu@t4vn.com\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003EGitHub Issues: \u003Ca data-router-slot=\u0022disabled\u0022 href=\u0022https://github.com/T4VN/uTPro/issues\u0022 target=\u0022_blank\u0022 type=\u0022external\u0022\u003E\u003Cu\u003EuTPro Issues\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/a\u003E (use \u0022security\u0022 label)\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003C/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003EWe aim to respond within 48 hours of receiving your report.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EPlease do \u003Cstrong\u003Enot\u003C/strong\u003E disclose security vulnerabilities publicly until we have had a chance to address them.\u003C/p\u003E"
                    }
                  }
                ]
              }
            ],
            "settingsData": [],
            "expose": [
              {
                "contentKey": "b0146e85-c0a7-4be4-9b1e-f5f56dc37077",
                "culture": "en-US",
                "segment": null
              }
            ],
            "layout": {
              "Umbraco.BlockList": [
                {
                  "contentKey": "b0146e85-c0a7-4be4-9b1e-f5f56dc37077",
                  "contentUdi": null,
                  "settingsKey": null,
                  "settingsUdi": null
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "alias": "description",
          "culture": "en-US",
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Thank you for helping us improve the security and reliability of uTPro."
        },
        {
          "alias": "title",
          "culture": "en-US",
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Reporting a Vulnerability"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
