        },
        {
          "alias": "title",
          "culture": "vi-VN",
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Ch\u00EDnh s\u00E1ch b\u1EA3o m\u1EADt"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "contentTypeKey": "7933a097-e795-4929-9746-d802b4ed8595",
      "key": "c127f280-7b31-4f58-ab15-9e2d587ae892",
      "values": [
        {
          "alias": "content",
          "culture": "vi-VN",
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": {
            "contentData": [
              {
                "contentTypeKey": "be80a795-b398-4baa-860a-ee68b7124f11",
                "key": "06845bca-11ac-44a4-9f79-6f08ca6c544b",
                "values": [
                  {
                    "alias": "richtext",
                    "culture": "vi-VN",
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": {
                      "blocks": {
                        "contentData": [],
                        "settingsData": [],
                        "expose": [],
                        "layout": {}
                      },
                      "markup": "\u003Cp\u003EuTPro bao g\u1ED3m c\u00E1c bi\u1EC7n ph\u00E1p t\u0103ng c\u01B0\u1EDDng b\u1EA3o m\u1EADt sau \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c c\u00E0i \u0111\u1EB7t s\u1EB5n:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EHTTP Security Headers\u003C/strong\u003E: X-Content-Type-Options, X-Frame-Options, Referrer-Policy, Permissions-Policy\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EHSTS\u003C/strong\u003E: Strict-Transport-Security trong m\u00F4i tr\u01B0\u1EDDng s\u1EA3n xu\u1EA5t (1 n\u0103m, bao g\u1ED3m SubDomains)\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESecure Sessions\u003C/strong\u003E: Cookie HttpOnly, Secure, SameSite=Strict\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ERequest Limits\u003C/strong\u003E: T\u1EA3i l\u00EAn t\u1ED1i \u0111a 128MB, b\u1EA3o v\u1EC7 ch\u1ED1ng l\u1EA1i t\u1EA3i tr\u1ECDng qu\u00E1 l\u1EDBn\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EDomain Policy\u003C/strong\u003E: Danh s\u00E1ch cho ph\u00E9p t\u00EAn mi\u1EC1n c\u00F3 th\u1EC3 c\u1EA5u h\u00ECnh v\u1EDBi kh\u1EDBp k\u00FD t\u1EF1 \u0111\u1EA1i di\u1EC7n\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EData Protection\u003C/strong\u003E: Kh\u00F3a m\u00E3 h\u00F3a v\u1EDBi v\u00F2ng xoay t\u1EF1 \u0111\u1ED9ng 90 ng\u00E0y\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EXSS Prevention\u003C/strong\u003E: Gi\u00E1 tr\u1ECB th\u1EBB meta \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c m\u00E3 h\u00F3a HTML trong k\u1EBFt qu\u1EA3 SEO\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EError Pages\u003C/strong\u003E: noindex/nofollow \u0111\u1EC3 ng\u0103n c\u00F4ng c\u1EE5 t\u00ECm ki\u1EBFm l\u1EADp ch\u1EC9 m\u1EE5c c\u00E1c trang l\u1ED7i\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003C/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E"
                    }
                  }
                ]
              }
            ],
            "settingsData": [],
            "expose": [
              {
                "contentKey": "06845bca-11ac-44a4-9f79-6f08ca6c544b",
                "culture": "vi-VN",
                "segment": null
              }
            ],
            "layout": {
              "Umbraco.BlockList": [
                {
                  "contentKey": "06845bca-11ac-44a4-9f79-6f08ca6c544b",
                  "contentUdi": null,
                  "settingsKey": null,
                  "settingsUdi": null
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "alias": "title",
          "culture": "vi-VN",
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "C\u00E1c t\u00EDnh n\u0103ng b\u1EA3o m\u1EADt t\u00EDch h\u1EE3p"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "contentTypeKey": "7933a097-e795-4929-9746-d802b4ed8595",
      "key": "cecc7d1b-4654-4f5b-8bc4-21121955342c",
      "values": [
        {
          "alias": "content",
          "culture": "vi-VN",
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": {
            "contentData": [
              {
                "contentTypeKey": "be80a795-b398-4baa-860a-ee68b7124f11",
                "key": "3456915d-7070-4df8-aa32-7e1469b86b76",
                "values": [
                  {
                    "alias": "richtext",
                    "culture": "vi-VN",
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": {
                      "blocks": {
                        "contentData": [],
                        "settingsData": [],
                        "expose": [],
                        "layout": {}
                      },
                      "markup": "\u003Cp\u003EN\u1EBFu ph\u00E1t hi\u1EC7n l\u1ED7i b\u1EA3o m\u1EADt, b\u1EA1n vui l\u00F2ng kh\u00F4ng c\u00F4ng khai th\u00F4ng tin r\u1ED9ng r\u00E3i m\u00E0 h\u00E3y b\u00E1o c\u00E1o qua c\u00E1c k\u00EAnh ch\u00EDnh th\u1EE9c sau:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003EEmail: \u003Ca data-router-slot=\u0022disabled\u0022 href=\u0022mailto:thientu@t4vn.com\u0022 type=\u0022external\u0022\u003E\u003Cu\u003Ethientu@t4vn.com\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003EV\u1EA5n \u0111\u1EC1 tr\u00EAn GitHub: \u003Ca data-router-slot=\u0022disabled\u0022 href=\u0022https://github.com/T4VN/uTPro/issues\u0022 target=\u0022_blank\u0022 type=\u0022external\u0022\u003E\u003Cu\u003EuTPro Issues\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/a\u003E (s\u1EED d\u1EE5ng nh\u00E3n \u0022security\u0022)\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003C/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003ECh\u00FAng t\u00F4i s\u1EBD c\u1ED1 g\u1EAFng ph\u1EA3n h\u1ED3i trong v\u00F2ng 48 gi\u1EDD k\u1EC3 t\u1EEB khi nh\u1EADn \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c b\u00E1o c\u00E1o c\u1EE7a b\u1EA1n.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EVui l\u00F2ng \u003Cstrong\u003Ekh\u00F4ng\u003C/strong\u003E c\u00F4ng khai c\u00E1c l\u1ED7 h\u1ED5ng b\u1EA3o m\u1EADt cho \u0111\u1EBFn khi ch\u00FAng t\u00F4i c\u00F3 c\u01A1 h\u1ED9i kh\u1EAFc ph\u1EE5c ch\u00FAng.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E"
                    }
                  }
                ]
              }
            ],
            "settingsData": [],
            "expose": [
              {
                "contentKey": "3456915d-7070-4df8-aa32-7e1469b86b76",
                "culture": "vi-VN",
                "segment": null
              }
            ],
